# ── dependencies / build output ─────────────────────────────────────────────
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/out/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/target/
**/.deploy/

# ── secrets — NEVER commit (these hold live keys) ───────────────────────────
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
# (…but keep the documented templates)
!**/.env.example

# ── ZK circuit build artifacts (regenerate via `pnpm build`) ────────────────
xorr-stellar-contracts/circuits/build/
**/*.ptau
# NOTE: browser proving artifacts under xorr-core/public/circuits/ ARE committed.

# ── reference clones (not ours; per stellar-privacy/CLAUDE.md) ───────────────
stellar-privacy/packages/
stellar-privacy/references/

# ── misc ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
**/*.log
**/.claude/settings.local.json
npm-debug.log*
